        "content": "<p>Welcome to the Zulip chat, congratulations on nicely formatting your first post :)</p>\n<p>To start with your last question, you can use the tactic <code>classical</code> before the definition of <code>œÉ‚ÇÇ</code> to allow you to arbitrary case distinctions in <code>if</code>.</p>",
        "id": 340167494,
